Package swervelib.simulation.ironmaple.simulation.seasonspecific.rebuilt2026

Class RebuiltHub

java.lang.Object
swervelib.simulation.ironmaple.simulation.Goal
swervelib.simulation.ironmaple.simulation.seasonspecific.rebuilt2026.RebuiltHub
All Implemented Interfaces:
SimulatedArena.Simulatable
public class RebuiltHub extends Goal

Simulates a HUBs on the field.

This class simulates the HUBs on the field where FUELs can be scored. Whether it is active can be determined by using Arena2026Rebuilt.isActive(boolean)
